BUILDINGS; HOUSING -- LOS ANGELES; LOS ANGELES -- DEVELOPMENT AND 
REDEVELOPMENT; OFFICE BUILDINGS; VENICE (CA) -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; 
ROBBINS, ALAN; SNYDER, JEROME H 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
