CONFRONTATIONS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- TURKEY; BUSH, GEORGE; 
HUSSEIN, SADDAM; KUWAIT -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- TURKEY; OIL PIPELINES; UNITED 
