JORDAN -- IMMIGRATION; IRAQ -- EMIGRATION; RELOCATION OF PEOPLE; IRAQ -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; IRAQ -- TRAVEL 
RESTRICTIONS 
</P>
