</P>
<P>
Conditions: partly cloudy, afternoon thundershowers 
</P>
<P>
Leader: Rob Kish, 35, of Port Orange, Fla. 
</P>
<P>
Location: Athens, Texas, 1,883 miles into the race. 
</P>
