</P>
<P>
Heat 1 -- Matt Archbold (San Clemente), Kaipo Guerrero (Laguna Niguel). Heat 2 
-- Chuy Reyna (Oceanside), Brock Little (Haleiwa, Hawaii). Heat 3 -- Kelly 
Gibson (Hermosa Beach), John Sawvell (Oxnard). Heat 4 -- Chris Frohoff (Redondo 
Beach), Taylor Knox (Carlsbad). Heat 5 -- Rick Irons (Ocean Beach), Craig 
Bechtloff (Huntington Beach). Heat 6 -- Todd Jacobs (Manhattan Beach), Mike 
