<DOCID> 261183 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 11, 1990, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Home Design; Part N; Page 6; Column 1; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
